{"atom_id": "md_dmAG_ex_a021", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/AG/examples.md", "line_start": 22, "line_end": 22, "verbatim": "An identifier was assigned to the reversibility test and this identifier was used to be link data across the multiple SDTM domains in which the data are represented.", "parent_section": "§AG.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-05T22:30:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "md_dmAG_ex_a022", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/AG/examples.md", "line_start": 24, "line_end": 24, "verbatim": "The question as to whether a short-acting bronchodilator was administered in the 4 hours prior to the reversibility assessment is represented in the CM domain because this prior administration would have been for therapeutic effect, not as part of the procedure.", "parent_section": "§AG.2 [Example 2]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-05T22:30:00Z"}}
